WEBVTT

00:05.697 --> 00:08.537
<b>You protected me.{ep06@21:55}</b>

00:08.537 --> 00:11.537
<b>Mind your own business, shithead.{ep06@21:58}</b>

00:12.197 --> 00:17.127
<b>I'm sick of owing people stuff!{ep06@22:01}</b>

00:17.587 --> 00:20.597
<b>If we get out of this, I'm calling us even!{ep06@22:06}</b>

00:30.267 --> 00:31.517
<b>He did it!</b>

00:49.287 --> 00:52.827
<b>I knew you were still alive, Chainsaw!</b>

00:49.897 --> 00:51.287
<b>Die!</b>

00:59.687 --> 01:01.837
<b>Fuck!</b>

01:03.287 --> 01:05.227
<b>Full recovery!{seems like pulling his ignition cord again can activate some self-repair}{+drinking some blood}</b>

01:06.497 --> 01:08.097
<b>You're wasting your time, Chainsaw!</b>

01:11.387 --> 01:14.107
<b>You won't find my heart here!</b>

01:14.107 --> 01:17.437
<b>You can't kill me!{timing:korosu koto wa dekinai zo}</b>

01:26.817 --> 01:27.827
<b>He's a devil?</b>

01:28.277 --> 01:29.827
<b>Doesn't look good.</b>

01:30.337 --> 01:32.897
<b>Denji keeps losing blood.</b>

01:32.897 --> 01:36.207
<b>If he loses too much, the chainsaws retract.</b>

01:42.087 --> 01:44.887
<b>He's nowhere near as strong as he used to be!</b>

01:45.257 --> 01:46.007
<b>Pitiful!</b>

01:46.007 --> 01:46.757
<b>Chainsaw!</b>

02:01.887 --> 02:03.807
<b>The chainsaws retracted!{TLC: should be past tense}</b>

02:03.807 --> 02:05.567
<b>Not enough blood!</b>

02:05.567 --> 02:07.247
<b>You lose!</b>

02:07.247 --> 02:08.107
<b>Now die!</b>

02:08.107 --> 02:09.717
<b>Chainsaw!</b>

02:18.827 --> 02:21.827
<b>Your blood tastes like nasty ditch water!</b>

02:22.127 --> 02:25.837
<b>But drinking it while looking at your suffering faces,</b>

02:25.837 --> 02:29.507
<b>it's like having strawberry jam!</b>

02:31.987 --> 02:34.757
<b>You see, the hunters that the devils fear most{ep06@10:30 but without the "not the strongest or bravest" part, which causes a bit of a reorganization in the English version}</b>

02:38.657 --> 02:41.517
<b>are the crazy ones.{ep06@10:36 modified, see above}</b>

02:45.297 --> 02:47.777
<b>Sahara was of sound mind.</b>

02:48.777 --> 02:50.527
<b>And that's why he's dead now.</b>

02:50.937 --> 02:52.527
<b>Kinouchi too.</b>

02:52.527 --> 02:56.157
<b>As well as Subaru and Sasaki.</b>

02:56.507 --> 03:00.057
<b>People of sound mind feel fear
 when faced with an attacking devil.</b>

03:00.057 --> 03:02.937
<b>And that fear powers up the devil.</b>

03:04.337 --> 03:07.967
<b>How about Aki? Now that you've seen him in action.</b>

03:09.007 --> 03:09.917
<b>Is he of sound mind?</b>

03:10.247 --> 03:14.927
<b>Could anyone who's planning
 to kill the Gun bastard be of sound mind?</b>

03:15.537 --> 03:19.677
<b>You joined the Bureau
 for the same reason, didn't you?</b>

03:20.277 --> 03:23.027
<b>So are you also crazy?</b>

03:23.987 --> 03:25.307
<b>I'm not.</b>

03:25.787 --> 03:27.017
<b>I agree.</b>

03:27.017 --> 03:32.817
<b>But still, you and almost every other hunter
 all want to kill the Gun bastard.</b>

03:33.177 --> 03:36.007
<b>You're open, straightforward, and simple.</b>

03:36.007 --> 03:40.077
<b>And that's why the devils know how to scare you.</b>

03:40.577 --> 03:45.327
<b>But who knows what a crazy person is thinking?</b>

03:45.717 --> 03:49.057
<b>Just like us, devils fear what they can't understand.</b>

03:51.717 --> 03:53.967
<b>Master Kishibe, that's a lot of booze.</b>

03:53.967 --> 03:56.197
<b>See! Sound mind.</b>

03:56.197 --> 03:59.147
<b>But as time goes, you'll gradually get crazy.</b>

04:04.797 --> 04:09.297
<b>Though, as long as you're visiting your partners' graves every month, it's still a ways away.</b>

04:10.577 --> 04:12.097
<b>I'm off.</b>

04:12.097 --> 04:15.237
<b>Aki is still weak, so make sure to train him well.</b>

04:16.037 --> 04:17.617
<b>I'll do it gradually.</b>

04:18.327 --> 04:19.867
<b>That won't do.</b>

04:20.517 --> 04:24.237
<b>He's seriously gathering flesh pieces.</b>

04:24.237 --> 04:27.627
<b>It won't take him that long
 to get to the Gun bastard.</b>

04:42.747 --> 04:43.637
<b>No.</b>

04:43.927 --> 04:46.977
<b>No! No! No! No! No! No! No!</b>

04:48.857 --> 04:49.977
<b>No.</b>

04:50.687 --> 04:51.517
<b>Aki, listen.</b>

04:52.117 --> 04:54.887
<b>How about the two of us go private?</b>

04:55.877 --> 04:58.837
<b>I have an offer for pretty good money.</b>

04:58.837 --> 05:01.297
<b>We won't need to chase the Gun bastard.</b>

05:01.297 --> 05:03.767
<b>And we can eat lunch in a place like this.</b>

05:03.767 --> 05:06.167
<b>Maybe go see a movie after work sometimes.</b>

05:06.167 --> 05:08.137
<b>Doesn't sound like a bad life.</b>

05:09.447 --> 05:11.877
<b>I'll join you for drinks whenever you call.</b>

05:11.877 --> 05:14.877
<b>But I'm never going private.</b>

05:15.497 --> 05:17.097
<b>I'll take that dessert.{very similar to ep06@10:45 and referencing the same dessert thing}</b>

05:18.507 --> 05:21.017
<b>Give me a smoke in return, then.</b>

05:28.687 --> 05:32.897
<b><i>Aki will definitely die if we fight the Gun Devil.</i></b>

05:33.867 --> 05:36.787
<b><i>It's not because we're still too weak.</i></b>

05:36.787 --> 05:40.307
<b><i>And it's not because it can kill
 hundreds of people almost instantly.</i></b>

05:41.447 --> 05:46.657
<b><i>It's because Aki is cool and serious and kind.</i></b>

05:47.157 --> 05:49.347
<b><i>He's a normal person.</i></b>

05:50.947 --> 05:51.667
<b><i>But...</i></b>

05:53.417 --> 05:55.167
<b>Eat this!</b>

06:03.387 --> 06:05.767
<b>I-I did it?</b>

06:11.487 --> 06:12.687
<b><i>...this boy...</i></b>

06:13.487 --> 06:15.437
<b>I've got this figured out!</b>

06:16.997 --> 06:19.817
<b>I cut you and you bleed.</b>

06:20.317 --> 06:23.817
<b>I drink your blood and heal.</b>

06:23.817 --> 06:27.997
<b>It's a perpetual motion machine!{how does Denji know such big words?}</b>

06:28.967 --> 06:32.747
<b>Looks like I'm gonna win that Nobel prize!{lmao}</b>

06:35.937 --> 06:38.837
<b><i>This boy is so utterly crazy</i></b>

06:39.447 --> 06:42.087
<b><i>that he might actually manage to kill the Gun bastard!</i></b>

07:09.147 --> 07:11.117
<b>Aki, you still alive?</b>

07:14.777 --> 07:15.937
<b>How long...</b>

07:16.777 --> 07:18.627
<b>How long have they been going?</b>

07:19.347 --> 07:22.757
<b>I think it's been about three days.</b>

07:23.457 --> 07:25.007
<b>Meowy...</b>

07:25.487 --> 07:28.637
<b>Let's all go drinking.</b>

07:29.347 --> 07:32.767
<b>It's over, so I want some shut-eye.</b>

07:34.057 --> 07:35.767
<b>It's over?</b>

07:37.577 --> 07:40.027
<b>{timing:kore ga watashi no kyuusho desu}This is my weak spot.</b>

07:40.467 --> 07:43.277
<b>{timing:watashi no shinzou desu}It's my heart.</b>

07:40.947 --> 07:42.437
<b>{timing:hayaku koroshite kudasai}Please kill me.</b>

07:43.277 --> 07:45.157
<b>{timing:mou itai no muri}I can't take the pain any more.</b>

07:44.087 --> 07:45.157
<b>{timing:itee}It hurts!</b>

07:45.157 --> 07:47.787
<b>That all you got?!</b>

07:47.787 --> 07:52.157
<b>But it was so fun! Like being at the pool!</b>

08:03.307 --> 08:04.717
<b>Made it out...</b>

08:07.947 --> 08:10.577
<b>We got a piece of the Gun Devil too.</b>

08:10.577 --> 08:11.867
<b>And it's sunny outside.</b>

08:11.867 --> 08:14.347
<b>I feel like I just took a dump.</b>

08:14.697 --> 08:16.667
<b>Like I'm floating.</b>

08:18.777 --> 08:19.977
<b>Got you.</b>

08:21.567 --> 08:22.737
<b>He fell asleep.</b>

08:23.487 --> 08:26.487
<b>He did keep cutting up the devil
 without any sleep for days.</b>

08:28.467 --> 08:31.737
<b>We'll take Aki and Denji to a hospital.</b>

08:32.157 --> 08:34.617
<b>The two of you, go report back.</b>

08:42.937 --> 08:44.997
<b>New recruit welcome party?</b>

08:44.997 --> 08:45.507
<b>Yeah.</b>

08:45.897 --> 08:48.727
<b>We've never really gathered the whole Fourth Division.</b>

08:48.727 --> 08:53.697
<b>Let's build some bonds
 and solve some of our problems.</b>

08:53.697 --> 08:54.757
<b>Problems?</b>

08:54.757 --> 08:59.897
<b>Well, Kobeni and Arai
 are thinking of quitting the Bureau.</b>

09:00.187 --> 09:02.647
<b>It's probably not just about their fresh trauma,</b>

09:02.647 --> 09:05.397
<b>but also regrets over wanting to kill Denji.</b>

09:06.257 --> 09:08.777
<b>You wanted to kill him too, Himeno.</b>

09:08.777 --> 09:10.077
<b>Right?!</b>

09:10.077 --> 09:13.397
<b>And those newbies want to quit
 over something like that.</b>

09:13.397 --> 09:16.287
<b>Why not just live without any shame?</b>

09:17.087 --> 09:20.537
<b>If we drink together, we can just apologize to Denji,</b>

09:20.537 --> 09:22.887
<b>and also convince Kobeni and Arai to stay.</b>

09:22.887 --> 09:24.337
<b>You just want to drink, don't you?</b>

09:25.257 --> 09:26.547
<b>Teehee.{or whatever fits a smug smile}</b>

09:26.547 --> 09:29.297
<b>I found a flesh piece, though it's tiny.</b>

09:29.787 --> 09:32.437
<b>If we go drinking, it has to be this week.</b>

09:32.437 --> 09:33.927
<b>What? How come?</b>

09:34.297 --> 09:37.337
<b>If we're going drinking,
 I'd like to go with Makima.</b>

09:44.517 --> 09:47.197
<b>And next week she goes to Kyoto.</b>

09:47.197 --> 09:51.317
<b>She'll be requesting backup
 on account of Denji being targeted by a devil.</b>

09:51.617 --> 09:53.627
<b>So if we're doing it, this week is the time.</b>

09:56.517 --> 09:57.827
<b>Be honest,</b>

09:58.297 --> 10:00.457
<b>what do you think Denji is?</b>

10:02.207 --> 10:05.927
<b>That devil there seemed to know him.</b>

10:05.927 --> 10:07.967
<b>And I've never seen anyone change like that.</b>

10:08.277 --> 10:12.717
<b>But the most mysterious thing
 is that Makima is worried about him.</b>

10:14.717 --> 10:18.887
<b>She usually travels all over,
 but lately she's been staying in Tokyo.</b>

10:18.887 --> 10:20.797
<b>It's because he's here, isn't it?</b>

10:21.447 --> 10:24.357
<b>Perhaps because she knows his secret.</b>

10:28.477 --> 10:30.357
<b>Guess I'll get her drunk and ask her.</b>

10:32.937 --> 10:34.367
<b>Cheers!</b>

10:34.367 --> 10:36.737
<b>{bg, Denji}Ah, that smells so good!</b>

10:38.237 --> 10:40.737
<b>Man, that's a lifetime's worth of this stuff.{bg, Denji}{can't quite make out what he says. something "mou isshou ???nee tte kore"}{TLC, CCs: もう一生 食えんじゃねえか これ}{"I'll never be able to eat this again"}</b>

10:38.247 --> 10:39.787
<b>{bg, Himeno}That hit the spot!</b>

