10:51.047 --> 10:52.387
<b>This is good.</b>

10:52.387 --> 10:54.237
<b>It's my first drink in six months.</b>

10:54.237 --> 10:56.677
<b>I just drink at home now and then.</b>

10:56.677 --> 10:58.367
<b>Move!</b>

10:58.367 --> 11:00.057
<b>All the sashimi is mine!</b>

11:00.397 --> 11:02.557
<b>What's this? Looks yummy!</b>

11:03.677 --> 11:05.057
<b>Sorry,</b>

11:05.427 --> 11:07.317
<b>I got a bit lost.</b>

11:07.617 --> 11:10.187
<b>Kobe! Kobe! Come sit here!</b>

11:10.517 --> 11:12.317
<b>Makima said she'd be late.</b>

11:14.467 --> 11:15.867
<b>Three parfaits, please.</b>

11:15.867 --> 11:19.447
<b>Also, three orders of mochi balls.</b>

11:20.297 --> 11:23.297
<b>I've never had food this good.</b>

11:23.297 --> 11:26.487
<b>I suppose you spend
 most of your money on your family.</b>

11:26.487 --> 11:27.517
<b>Eat up well.</b>

11:27.517 --> 11:28.917
<b>Hands off, you thief!</b>

11:28.917 --> 11:31.217
<b>All the fried chicken is mine!</b>

11:31.877 --> 11:35.037
<b>You couldn't bring your fiend, Fushi?</b>

11:35.037 --> 11:37.877
<b>He'd cause too much commotion.</b>

11:37.877 --> 11:41.597
<b>You're lucky yours is pretty reasonable.</b>

11:41.987 --> 11:45.477
<b>Come on, boy! You're still young.
 Order more stuff! Eat!</b>

11:45.477 --> 11:46.357
<b>Ah, shit.</b>

