11:53.237 --> 11:55.597
<b>By the way, what about that kiss?</b>

11:55.597 --> 11:56.647
<b>Huh?</b>

11:56.647 --> 11:57.947
<b>Oh!</b>

11:58.287 --> 12:00.897
<b>I'm too embarrassed to do it sober.</b>

12:00.897 --> 12:02.617
<b>Wait until I'm more drunk.</b>

12:05.117 --> 12:07.807
<b>I'll give you a really thick one,</b>

12:07.807 --> 12:11.507
<b>so forgive everyone for trying to kill you, okay?</b>

12:11.507 --> 12:14.927
<b>Sure, I super forgive you! Totally!</b>

12:15.337 --> 12:19.467
<b>This is a newbie welcome party, so as a newbie,
 stand up and introduce yourself!</b>

12:19.467 --> 12:22.217
<b>Say your name, your age,
 and the devil you've contracted with.</b>

12:22.667 --> 12:25.837
<b>Don't say the devil in public.</b>

12:25.837 --> 12:29.417
<b>You should only show your cards
 to people you trust.</b>

12:29.417 --> 12:31.927
<b>Antisocial as usual.</b>

12:31.927 --> 12:35.147
<b>Ah, it should be fine! Don't worry!</b>

12:35.627 --> 12:37.627
<b>I want to hear about your hobbies!</b>

12:37.627 --> 12:39.527
<b>They say a lot about a person.</b>

12:39.927 --> 12:41.327
<b>I'm Denji.</b>

12:41.327 --> 12:43.317
<b>I'm sixteen, I think.{he throws in a "tashika", is he, like... just "pretty sure" he's 16? does he not know for sure? or is he just too drunk to remember immediately?}{TLC: he's just not sure when he was born}</b>

12:43.317 --> 12:46.537
<b>My hobbies are eating and sleeping.</b>

12:43.317 --> 12:44.007
<b>Huh?</b>

12:47.567 --> 12:48.667
<b>Wow! So young!</b>

12:49.567 --> 12:51.927
<b>You didn't drink any booze, did you?!</b>

12:51.927 --> 12:52.547
<b>Tea!</b>

12:53.127 --> 12:55.167
<b>I'm Arai Hirokazu!</b>

12:55.167 --> 12:56.177
<b>Twenty-two!</b>

12:56.177 --> 12:57.677
<b>My contracted devil is the Fox!</b>

12:58.057 --> 12:59.677
<b>My hobby is haiku poetry!</b>

13:00.367 --> 13:02.807
<b>Same devil as Haya-man?</b>

13:03.147 --> 13:06.117
<b>The Fox Devil is friendly towards humans,</b>

13:06.117 --> 13:08.507
<b>so it forms contracts with many devil hunters.</b>

13:08.507 --> 13:11.707
<b>Only handsome men can use the Fox head.</b>

13:11.707 --> 13:13.817
<b>It likes pretty faces.</b>

13:15.447 --> 13:17.367
<b>I'm Higashiyama Kobeni.</b>

13:17.367 --> 13:18.657
<b>I'm twenty.</b>

13:18.657 --> 13:21.887
<b>The devil I'm contracted with is... a secret.</b>

13:21.887 --> 13:24.327
<b>My hobby is eating delicious food.</b>

13:25.447 --> 13:26.907
<b>Her clothes are pretty cute, no?</b>

13:26.907 --> 13:27.457
<b>Yeah.</b>

13:27.837 --> 13:29.957
<b>These are all hand-me-downs from my sister.</b>

13:30.327 --> 13:33.707
<b>{Himeno}Hold on. Where's Fushi's newbie?</b>

13:30.327 --> 13:33.707
<b>{bg}Kobeni has eight siblings. Quite something.</b>

13:34.087 --> 13:36.717
<b>Unfortunately, he died yesterday.</b>

13:38.707 --> 13:44.217
<b>{this is a scuffed attempt at a Buddhist "prayer" for the dead. maybe}May his soul rest in peace. Amen and all that.</b>

13:44.217 --> 13:45.967
<b>She's wasted already.</b>

13:47.767 --> 13:49.727
<b>Do people die that easily?</b>

13:50.357 --> 13:53.607
<b>The Bureau gets the devils
 that the civilian hunters can't handle.</b>

13:54.197 --> 13:56.337
<b>They do die quite a lot.</b>

13:56.337 --> 13:58.987
<b>No one who started around when I did is still here.</b>

13:59.277 --> 14:03.237
<b>But Denji won't die because he wants to kiss me.</b>

14:04.197 --> 14:05.117
<b>Yeah!</b>

14:05.567 --> 14:08.017
<b>When Himeno gets drunk, she starts kissing people.</b>

14:08.017 --> 14:09.057
<b>Huh?!</b>

14:09.057 --> 14:12.877
<b>She's kissed everyone here, apart from the newbies.</b>

14:12.877 --> 14:14.747
<b>You can't get away from her.</b>

14:17.697 --> 14:18.877
<b><i>Kiss secured!</i></b>

14:21.917 --> 14:25.347
<b>I'm getting my first kiss today...</b>

14:25.797 --> 14:26.807
<b>A kiss?</b>

14:27.667 --> 14:29.637
<b>Makima!</b>

14:29.637 --> 14:32.477
<b>Excuse me, can I get a beer?</b>

14:33.017 --> 14:35.607
<b>Miss Makima, please have this seat.</b>

14:37.927 --> 14:40.357
<b>First time I've seen her in person.</b>

14:42.447 --> 14:44.737
<b>Denji, are you going to kiss someone?</b>

14:44.737 --> 14:45.737
<b>Hell no!</b>

14:45.737 --> 14:46.757
<b>What?!</b>

14:46.757 --> 14:49.117
<b>Denji, don't you want to kiss me?</b>

14:49.117 --> 14:50.117
<b>Hell yeah!</b>

14:53.747 --> 14:56.127
<b>Excuse me, can I get another beer?</b>

14:58.517 --> 15:00.187
<b>So, kissing, huh?</b>

15:00.187 --> 15:04.007
<b><i>I don't want Makima to see me kissing Himeno.</i></b>

15:04.447 --> 15:06.237
<b>You don't want a smooch?</b>

15:06.237 --> 15:10.137
<b><i>But just as much, I want a kiss with tongue!</i></b>

15:10.707 --> 15:13.147
<b><i>I need to change the topic!</i></b>

15:13.497 --> 15:18.187
<b>Makima! I got one of those Gun Devil thingies!</b>

15:18.187 --> 15:19.917
<b>Yes. I heard about that.</b>

15:19.917 --> 15:21.397
<b>You're doing great.</b>

15:21.847 --> 15:26.867
<b>We didn't use to find devils
 with flesh pieces this often.</b>

15:26.867 --> 15:29.507
<b>The devils have been acting weirdly lately.</b>

15:29.507 --> 15:32.157
<b>Like that one that was targeting Denji.</b>

15:32.637 --> 15:36.277
<b>Do you know something about Denji
 that you're not telling us?{end-time could be snapped to keyframe -Pik}</b>

15:38.347 --> 15:39.417
<b>{bg, Power}Give me that too!</b>

15:41.667 --> 15:42.667
<b>{bg, Power}That is mine too!</b>

15:46.767 --> 15:49.177
<b>I'll tell you if you can drink more than me.</b>

15:51.657 --> 15:53.437
<b>Excuse me, can I get two beers?</b>

15:54.947 --> 15:56.997
<b>I want in on that!</b>

15:56.997 --> 15:58.317
<b>One more beer!</b>

15:58.317 --> 16:00.437
<b>Horse sashimi! Fried chicken! Horse sashimi!</b>

16:00.767 --> 16:01.897
<b>Fried chicken!</b>

16:07.807 --> 16:08.927
<b>{bg, Power}That one is good too!</b>

16:08.927 --> 16:11.407
<b>Excuse me, can I get another beer?</b>

16:11.807 --> 16:14.017
<b>I'm actually pretty impressed with you, Power.</b>

16:14.017 --> 16:17.837
<b>Very few fiends can restrain their murderous instincts.</b>

16:17.837 --> 16:20.417
<b>That is because I have a high IQ.</b>

16:20.417 --> 16:23.607
<b>Is that what it depends on?</b>

16:23.607 --> 16:25.997
<b>How high is yours?</b>

16:25.997 --> 16:26.797
<b>100?</b>

16:26.797 --> 16:28.787
<b>Is 100 high?</b>

16:28.787 --> 16:31.717
<b>I think I got about 100 too.</b>

16:31.717 --> 16:33.057
<b>120, then.</b>

16:33.487 --> 16:36.087
<b>I think you had a pretty high score, right, Fushi?</b>

16:36.087 --> 16:37.827
<b>Yes. 134.</b>

16:37.827 --> 16:41.187
<b>You remember the exact number.
 Must be pretty proud of it.</b>

16:41.187 --> 16:44.057
<b>What was mine? 500?</b>

16:44.057 --> 16:44.567
<b>1000?</b>

16:46.547 --> 16:47.197
<b>Huh?</b>

16:50.057 --> 16:50.947
<b>Oh, my.</b>

16:55.577 --> 16:56.577
<b><i>She can see us.</i></b>

16:56.907 --> 16:58.207
<b><i>Makima is looking.</i></b>

16:58.737 --> 17:01.587
<b><i>But what is this sensation? The tongue?</i></b>

16:59.167 --> 17:00.087
<b>Kissing.</b>

17:01.587 --> 17:02.807
<b><i>It's nice!</i></b>

17:02.807 --> 17:04.167
<b><i>Soft! So soft!</i></b>

17:04.167 --> 17:06.087
<b><i>Is this her tongue, too?</i></b>

17:06.087 --> 17:08.267
<b><i>It's melting inside my mouth.</i></b>

17:08.267 --> 17:09.967
<b><i>It's not her tongue!</i></b>

17:10.627 --> 17:11.967
<b><i>It's puke!</i></b>

17:14.727 --> 17:16.727
<b>Well, that'll scar him for life.</b>

17:17.077 --> 17:18.237
<b>Oh, dear.</b>

17:18.237 --> 17:20.727
<b>Excuse me, can we get something to clean up with?</b>

17:20.727 --> 17:23.827
<b>That's nasty! Real nasty!</b>

17:24.637 --> 17:25.107
<b>Huh?</b>

17:25.107 --> 17:29.607
<b>Denji is used to swallowing
 anything that could be nourishment!</b>

17:35.067 --> 17:36.077
<b>Pochita!</b>

17:36.687 --> 17:38.327
<b>This looks edible!</b>

17:48.357 --> 17:49.467
<b>Look, Pochita!</b>

17:49.827 --> 17:52.707
<b>The rats are all hanging around some drunk's puke.</b>

17:52.707 --> 17:55.217
<b>Can't believe they're eating puke.</b>

17:55.527 --> 17:57.847
<b>Makes me ashamed to be a mammal!</b>

18:01.347 --> 18:06.107
<b>Man, Himeno needs to learn some self-control.</b>

18:10.857 --> 18:13.247
<b>I'm good at helping with vomit, right?</b>

18:10.857 --> 18:10.897
